        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You're an incredibly talented storyteller, making legends come to life. You gain @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.spells.Item.Illusory Scene] as a 6th-rank occult innate spell. You can cast this spell once per day. When you cast <em>illusory scene</em> in this way, the spell automatically adapts to suit its audience. A deaf creature that witnesses the illusion additionally sees the characters in the scene visually signing their dialogue. A blind creature that witnesses the illusion additionally hears an audio description of the scene. A deafblind creature that witnesses the illusion additionally receives a psychic impression of the scene and its dialogue in their mind.</p>"
